1.0.name: wordpress/chartbeat
1.0.description: Chartbeat is a real-time data service for your website, social streams, and iOS apps. Once you become a Chartbeat member, you can use this plugin to automatically add the necessary JavaScript to your WordPress blog. After installing the plugin, you’ll instantly see your site’s traffic, and audience behaviors.
